                        <p>Get your personalized subdomain with complete data isolation. Your students, quizzes, and content are completely separate from other teachers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe feature-icon"></i>
