                        <p>Create quizzes in English, Spanish, French, and Kannada. Our advanced parsing engine understands different question formats automatically.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Comprehensive Analytics</h4>
                        <p>Track student progress, quiz performance, and learning outcomes with detailed analytics and reporting tools.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Easy Content Management</h4>
                        <p>Upload PDFs, Word documents, and PowerPoint files. Share study materials with grade-level filtering.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Secure & Scalable</h4>
                        <p>Enterprise-grade security with automatic backups, SSL encryption, and scalable infrastructure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>

